Class JobService

  • java.lang.Object
    • businesslogic.JobService

  • public class JobService
extends java.lang.Object
    Job Service handles all the operations regarding the Job Object, including inserting, deleting, updating, allocating and building.

        description - description of job as a String

        dateFinished - parse-able end date of job as a String

        status - status of job as a String
        Returns:
        status of insertion into database
